name: REG_DI_ALL
description:
Digital inputs. 
Coil 11201: input 1. 
Coil 11202: input 2. 
Coil 11203: input 3. 
Coil 11204: input 4. 
Coil 11205: input 5. 
Coil 11206: input 6. Note: read only! 
Coil 11207: input 7. 
Coil value 0: input inactive. 
Coil value 1: input active.

name: REG_DI_EXT_RUNNING_SPEED_LVL
description:
Fan speed level during extended running: 
0: Off 
1: Low speed 
2: Normal speed
3: High speed

name: REG_DI1_SF_LVL
description: Supply fan speed level at activated digital input 1

name: REG_DI1_EF_LVL
description: Extract fan speed level at activated digital input 1

name: REG_DI2_SF_LVL
description: Supply fan speed level at activated digital input 2

name: REG_DI2_EF_LVL
description: Extract fan speed level at activated digital input 2

name: REG_DI3_SF_LVL
description: Supply fan speed level at activated digital input 3

name: REG_DI3_EF_LVL
description: Extract fan speed level at activated digital input 3
